column5:
Remember this?

I ran into a contractor at the north launch ( by the marina) and he said they were fixing that launch and the government dock launch this week. I'm sure a lot of trailer owners will be happy!
Hopefuly those lonely wet shoes find a good home.
Actually, Nipfisher just told me it'll be open on friday... Still good news

Those are my Red Head sandals. Not lonley and the bast sandals I've ever owned. I had them off to help them out. That launch is closed until Friday but the one on Big Moose Rd. is all fixed and is terrific. Nice to have deep water at the launch you can drive on and off your trailer.
